FBIS3-26839 "drchi031_m_94005" FBIS-CHI-94-031 Document Type:Daily Report 15 Feb 1994 Military Guizhou Military Unit Conducts Satellite Test HK1102101994 Guiyang Guizhou People's Radio Network in Mandarin 2300 GMT 8 Feb 94 HK1102101994 Guiyang Guizhou People's Radio Network Language: Mandarin Article Type:BFN [Text] Yesterday evening [8 February], officers and soldiers of a Guizhou-stationed armed forces unit under the Commmission for National Defense Science, Technology, and Industry satisfactorily completed a tracking test on China's No. 4 scientific experimental satellite. To fulfill this test, three months ago this armed forces unit already made the necessary arrangements, assigned technological personnel to their posts, given them training, and examined and repaired the equipment.
